\begin_layout Standard
So we have tested 3 different cases for the GPU:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
GPU with shared memory and with memory copy overhead
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

From Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
